<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Professor Login | DocSec</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #020617;
      --card: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.96);
      --border: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.6);
      --accent: #6366f1;
      --text: #e5e7eb;
      --muted: #9ca3af;
      --radius-xl: 20px;
      --shadow: 0 18px 55px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.98);
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "SF Pro Text", sans-serif;
      min-height: 100vh;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(129, 140, 248, 0.25), transparent 55%),
        radial-gradient(circle at bottom, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.2), transparent 55%),
        #020617;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 20px;
      color: var(--text);
    }
    .card {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 430px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: linear-gradient(150deg, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.97), rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9));
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding: 18px 18px 16px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .card::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: -40%;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 0 0, rgba(129, 140, 248, 0.25), transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 100% 100%, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.25), transparent 60%);
      opacity: 0.9;
      pointer-events: none;
      filter: blur(20px);
    }
    .card-inner {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 20px;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }
    .sub {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }
    .badge {
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.8);
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.95);
      padding: 3px 9px;
      font-size: 10px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    }
    .field {
      margin-top: 8px;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    label {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 3px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }
    .input {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 8px 10px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.7);
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9);
      color: var(--text);
      outline: none;
      font-size: 12px;
      transition: border 0.18s ease-out, box-shadow 0.18s ease-out, background 0.18s ease-out;
    }
    .input:focus {
      border-color: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.9);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.65);
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.98);
    }
    .helper {
      font-size: 10px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 3px;
    }
    .primary-btn {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 9px 10px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.9);
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #0ea5e9);
      color: #e5e7eb;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 500;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 6px;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(76, 81, 191, 0.9);
      transition: transform 0.18s ease-out, box-shadow 0.18s ease-out;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .primary-btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 22px 50px rgba(76, 81, 191, 1);
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--muted);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 6px;
    }
    .footer span.accent {
      color: #a5b4fc;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-inner">
      <div class="header">
        <div>
          <h1>Professor Login</h1>
          <p class="sub">Upload PDFs and track how students interact with them.</p>
        </div>
        <span class="badge">Professor</span>
      </div>

      <form action="/prof/login" method="POST">
        <div class="field">
          <label for="email">Academic Email</label>
          <input
            id="email"
            type="email"
            name="email"
            class="input"
            placeholder="e.g., prof.sharma@college.edu"
            required
          />
        </div>

        <div class="field">
          <label for="password">Password</label>
          <input
            id="password"
            type="password"
            name="password"
            class="input"
            placeholder="Your secure password"
            required
          />
          <p class="helper">Use the login credentials provided by admin.</p>
        </div>

        <button type="submit" class="primary-btn">
          Go to dashboard
          <span>â†—</span>
        </button>
      </form>

      <div class="footer">
        <span>Students will only see PDFs you share with their class.</span>
        <span class="accent">You see open stats, they just see notes.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
